    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i was reading something earlier that basically said we don't really have a choice if we want to hit net zero targets, and that renewables alone won't cut it because of the grid stability issues. do you think that's a fair assessment, or is that just one way of looking at it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
